<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10099431>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Wing venation of Hennigmatidae (holotypes): A, Kuperwoodia benefica Lukashevich, 1995; B, Anemeca liya Shcherbakov, 1995; С, Metatrichopteridium cladistorum (Shcherbakov, 1995); D, Daohennigma panops Lukashevich et al., 2006; modified after Shcherbakov et al., 1995 (A–C) and Lukashevich et al., 2006 (D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10099431/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10099441>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Basiala of Hennigmatinae: A, B, Trihennigma zavattierii gen. et sp. nov.: holotype MCNAM-PI 24607, part and inverted counterpart; C, Metatrichopteridium cladistorum (Shcherbakov, 1995): holotype PIN 3965/2789. Abbreviation: ai— alular incision." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10099441/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10099443>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Proximal part of the wing of Metatrichopteridium cladistorum (Shcherbakov, 1995): holotype PIN 3965/2789: A, drawing; B, SEM image (SE). Abbreviation: ai—alular incision." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10099443/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10099437>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A, Metatrichopteridium cladistorum (Shcherbakov, 1995): holotype PIN 3965/2789; B, Daohennigma panops Lukashevich et al., 2006: holotype NIGPAS 133706." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10099437/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

